  "comment": "SB400IP Stage Blinder IP65 COB: The IP65 rated SB400IP Stage Blinder is a powerful LED lighting fixture with a rugged aluminium design featuring 4x 100W Chip-on-Board (COB) LEDs that combines two effects in its housing. In addition to a stage blinder, this fixture can also be used as a stroboscope. The SB400IP matches the blinding light output of a conventional Audience Blinder and can be controlled in standalone mode, sound activation mode or directly via DMX in a 4 or 8-channel mode. The LEDs feature up to a 60.000 hour life expectancy. The colour of the LEDs is warm white.\n\n",
